Some examples to test the INDI for Java Client library.

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AutoBLOBSaver
    A INDI Client that listens to a particular BLOB Element and saves it to a file whenever it is updated.
    SimpleINDIClient
    A simple INDI Client that listens to a particular INDI Server and prints any message received (listens to all possible events).
